01:48:34.041 --> 01:48:37.784
<i>It's not something I would've chosen
to do under the circumstances, but...</i>

01:50:36.296 --> 01:50:37.639
Hippie scum.

01:50:38.599 --> 01:50:40.670
Jarhead fuck.

01:50:44.404 --> 01:50:45.940
If you ever need a reference...

01:50:46.273 --> 01:50:47.616
What, you can...

01:50:47.774 --> 01:50:50.414
tell them how we destroyed
modern journalism together?

01:50:57.751 --> 01:50:59.697
